<li class='cover' id='bookCover_48549702'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/48549702-upstream"><img alt="Upstream: The Quest to Solve Problems Before They Happen" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1571690412l/48549702._SX98_.jpg" />
