      <div id="aboutAuthor" class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/author/show/39021.Chip_Heath">About Chip Heath</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class='bookAuthorProfile'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__topContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__photoContainer'>
<a href="/author/show/39021.Chip_Heath"><div class='bookAuthorProfile__photo' style='background-image: url(https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1374634334p3/39021.jpg);'></div>
</a></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__widgetContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__name'>
<a href="/author/show/39021.Chip_Heath">Chip Heath
</a></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__followerCount'>
1,142
followers
</div>

</div>
</div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer15575229903178815324">Chip Heath is the professor of Organizational Behavior in the Graduate School of Business at Stanford University.<br/>He received his B.S. degree in Industrial Engineering from Texas A&amp;M University and his Ph.D. in Psychology from Stanford.<br/><br/>He co-wrote a book titled <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/6570502.Switch_How_to_Change_Things_When_Change_Is_Hard' title='Switch How to Change Things When Change Is Hard by Chip Heath' rel='nofollow noopener'>Switch How to Change Things When Change Is Hard</a> with his brother <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/5722305.Dan_Heath__Chip_Heath' title='Dan Heath, Chip Heath' rel='nofollow noopener'>Dan Heath</a>.<br/> </span>
  <span id="freeText15575229903178815324" style="display:none">Chip Heath is the professor of Organizational Behavior in the Graduate School of Business at Stanford University.<br />He received his B.S. degree in Industrial Engineering from Texas A&amp;M University and his Ph.D. in Psychology from Stanford.<br /><br />He co-wrote a book titled <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/6570502.Switch_How_to_Change_Things_When_Change_Is_Hard" title="Switch How to Change Things When Change Is Hard by Chip Heath" rel="nofollow noopener">Switch How to Change Things When Change Is Hard</a> with his brother <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/5722305.Dan_Heath__Chip_Heath" title="Dan Heath, Chip Heath" rel="nofollow noopener">Dan Heath</a>.<br /> </span>
  <a data-text-id="15575229903178815324" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

</div>
</div>

